WEBVTT

00:08.425 --> 00:09.519
This is the kitchen.

00:09.653 --> 00:13.769
This is where we cook and eat breakfast, lunch and dinner.

00:13.883 --> 00:14.992
It is so clean and neat.

00:15.163 --> 00:18.010
This is the living room, we watch TV here.

00:18.507 --> 00:21.525
We flop on the sofa without a care.

00:21.827 --> 00:23.225
This is the bathroom.

00:23.335 --> 00:25.039
It keeps us clean and healthy.

00:25.121 --> 00:28.153
The basin and the tub and the little potty.

00:28.573 --> 00:31.519
This is the bedroom where we sleep.

00:31.783 --> 00:35.027
When the day is over, into my bed I creep.

